76561198083890768,Recommended,305960,12868228,"Posted: 9 November, 2014",all,*:･✯ Molly Golly ✯･:*,"if u have problems here is what they have seid to do:Getting into the game:1. Open Game2. Click CREATE DRAGON3. Create the dragon (don't forget a name in the upper left corner)4. Click NEW GAME5. Enter world name (does not save yet)6. Click on mapDeleted dragon problems:There are two different solutions I have seen so far. The first:1. Go to Program Files2. Open SteamApps3. Open Dragon4. Delete the Characters and Characters.drg filesOr:1. Open Steam Game Library2. Right click on Dragon: The Game3. Open Local Files tab4. Browse Local files, but don't do anything else yet.5. Uninstall the game from Steam6. Delete the Dragon folder from WinExplorer7. Delete the file from the Recyle Bin8. Reinstall Dragon"
